{
  "stem": "5654.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'll never forget, also, that we used to have walnuts.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we found a step ladder.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we walked, walked up a bit and we put the ladder against the tree.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And not knowing that downstairs, there was the farmer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It belonged, actually, to us, but he looked after the thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He stood there waiting for us to come down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We got the shock of our lives when he-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--when he was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, OK, you two.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Carry the ladder.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you're punished, you see?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we walked in front.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By the time he closed some gates, you see, we just dropped the ladder and then off we took.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they tried to, to find us in, in the dining room, when everybody used to be-- used to sit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when-- walnuts, you know, when they still got the-- what do you call?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That green-- before they're ripe, All your lips becomes brown.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And your teeth.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's him.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's him.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He used to pick us up like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I must say, that also, it was a religious home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So Shabbat was Shabbat with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to do the benching.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on various-- on many occasions, I was asked to do the benching.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, it, it it was really-- that's where I got my, my, my training in Yiddish [NON-ENGLISH], really.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- there was a bit of anti-Semitism, definitely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we often used to fight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to call us-- in French, it's called, you know, dirty Jew or something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, we used to gang-- they ganged up against us and we'd do the same thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that-- it was the norm in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
